bname <- c("b2")
sname <- 1
a <- c("b2_sp", "b2_jj", "b2_xj", "b2_n", "b2_center")
metri <- c("pd")
dt <- read_csv("/Users/placenameday/R study/edf_demo/data/processed/eye_tacking/ea/data/b2_info.csv")

fangfa

# 
dtc2 <- dt %>% filter(block_name==bname, stim==sname, AOI %in% a) %>%
  group_by(participant_phone, type, AOI) %>%
  summarise(fc=mean(!!sym(metri), na.rm=T), maas=mean(maas), tgjl=mean(tgjl), sas=mean(sas)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(fc)) %>%
  mutate(AOI=case_when(AOI == "b2_sp"~"sp",
                       AOI == "b2_jj"~"pos",
                       AOI == "b2_xj"~"neg",
                       AOI == "b2_n"~"ne",
                       AOI == "b2_star"~"star",
                       AOI == "b2_no_star"~"no_star",
                       AOI == "b2_center"~"center")) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  convert_as_factor(participant_phone, type,AOI) %>%
  select(participant_phone, type,AOI, tgjl, maas, sas, fc)


# 
outdata <- dtc2 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r <- anti_join(dtc2, outdata)
outdata2 <- dtb3_r %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r2 <- anti_join(dtb3_r, outdata2)
outdata3 <- dtb3_r2 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r3 <- anti_join(dtb3_r2, outdata3)
outdata4 <- dtb3_r3 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r4 <- anti_join(dtb3_r3, outdata4)
outdata5 <- dtb3_r4 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)


# 
mixed_maas = lmer(fc ~ maas+AOI+maas*AOI +  (1 | participant_phone)+(1|type), data = dtb3_r4)
mixed_sas = lmer(fc ~ sas+AOI+sas*AOI +  (1 | participant_phone)+(1|type), data = dtb3_r4)
mixed_two = lmer(fc ~ maas+sas+AOI+maas*sas+maas*AOI+sas*AOI +  (1 | participant_phone)+(1|type), data = dtb3_r4)

bname <- c("b2")
sname <- 2
a <- c("b2_star", "b2_no_star", "b2_center")
metri <- c("pd")
dt <- read_csv("/Users/placenameday/R study/edf_demo/data/processed/eye_tacking/ea/data/b2_info.csv")

fangfa

# 
dtc2 <- dt %>% filter(block_name==bname, stim==sname, AOI %in% a) %>%
  group_by(participant_phone, AOI) %>%
  summarise(fc=mean(!!sym(metri), na.rm=T), maas=mean(maas), tgjl=mean(tgjl), sas=mean(sas)) %>%
  filter(!is.na(fc)) %>%
  mutate(AOI=case_when(AOI == "b2_sp"~"sp",
                       AOI == "b2_jj"~"pos",
                       AOI == "b2_xj"~"neg",
                       AOI == "b2_n"~"ne",
                       AOI == "b2_star"~"star",
                       AOI == "b2_no_star"~"no_star",
                       AOI == "b2_center"~"center")) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  convert_as_factor(participant_phone, AOI) %>%
  select(participant_phone, AOI, tgjl, maas, sas, fc)


# 
outdata <- dtc2 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r <- anti_join(dtc2, outdata)
outdata2 <- dtb3_r %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r2 <- anti_join(dtb3_r, outdata2)
outdata3 <- dtb3_r2 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r3 <- anti_join(dtb3_r2, outdata3)
outdata4 <- dtb3_r3 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)
dtb3_r4 <- anti_join(dtb3_r3, outdata4)
outdata5 <- dtb3_r4 %>%
  group_by(AOI) %>%
  identify_outliers(fc)


# 
mixed_maas = lmer(fc ~ maas+AOI+maas*AOI + (1 | participant_phone), data = dtb3_r4)
mixed_sas = lmer(fc ~ sas*AOI + (1 | participant_phone), data = dtb3_r4)
mixed_two = lmer(fc ~ maas+sas+AOI+maas*sas+maas*AOI+sas*AOI + (1 | participant_phone), data = dtb3_r4)
